# Tools Summary

## All Tools at a Glance
| Tool | Install | Purpose |
|------|---------|---------|
| fping | sudo apt install fping | Host discovery |
| nmap | sudo apt install nmap | Port scanning |
| enum4linux-ng | sudo apt install enum4linux-ng | Full AD enumeration |
| rpcclient | sudo apt install samba-common-bin | RPC enumeration |
| ldapsearch | sudo apt install ldap-utils | LDAP enumeration |
| kerbrute | Download from GitHub | User validation |

